This ship first appears at the conclusion of "" (1986) and is the main setting in the subsequent Star Trek movies which use the original crew. The ship is ordered decommissioned at the end of "Star Trek VI: The Undiscovered Country". Paperwork included with the model kit indicated the ship was mothballed at the Memory Alpha ship museum. Outside other Star Trek book canon, the Shatnerverse novel "The Ashes of Eden" (1996) depicts the "Enterprise"-A's removal from the mothball fleet before being destroyed defending the planet Chal.
